    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom-quality condition since the day it was first driven off the lot. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, complemented by pristine alloy wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium leather seats still retain their factory-fresh scent and supple texture, with no signs of bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy at authorized service centers. We have a complete binder of service records documenting its pampered life. If you are looking for a collector-grade example that drives as perfectly as it looks, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
